Source: sonic-bmc-platform-aspeed
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Nexthop <opensource@nexthop.ai>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 3.9.6

Package: sonic-bmc-platform-aspeed
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3
Description: SONiC BMC platform support for Aspeed AST2700
 This package provides BMC-specific systemd services, scripts, and
 SONiC Platform API implementation for Aspeed AST2700 BMC platform, including:
  - BMC initialization
  - Chassis management
  - Thermal sensor monitoring (16 ADC channels)
  - Fan monitoring and control (16 TACH inputs, 9 PWM outputs)
  - Hardware watchdog control
  - Reboot cause detection

